 going on with his muscles or nerves.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.085632,0.12411,0.13101,0.12613,0.11223,0.098466,0.084277,0.069162,0.057913,0.049636,0.038329,0.023113],"unified_progress":[0.073451,0.11531,0.12191,0.13029,0.10635,0.093486,0.084933,0.07507,0.064796,0.055938,0.045435,0.033034]},{"section":3,"text":"Now, let's think about what could cause these symptoms.","dimension":5,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.018876,0.072996,0.11201,0.12946,0.12666,0.11739,0.10304,0.092859,0.08174,0.072306,0.050352,0.022313],"unified_progress":[0.041197,0.081432,0.092279,0.12026,0.10618,0.095034,0.098944,0.087168,0.080105,0.084254,0.064906,0.048245]},{"section":4,"text":"Muscle weakness and a waddling gait make me wonder if it's something that affects the muscles directly.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038336,0.065414,0.086803,0.1016,0.10621,0.10908,0.10701,0.1007,0.092579,0.087264,0.067613,0.037383],"unified_progress":[0.042721,0.072411,0.087674,0.096068,0.10023,0.10069,0.10145,0.097298,0.090908,0.085057,0.070903,0.054591]},{"section":5,"text":"Hmm, there's also hypertrophy of the calf muscles.","dimension":7,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.030641,0.058777,0.078573,0.095142,0.10455,0.10967,0.11044,0.1063,0.10268,0.09817,0.070685,0.034361],"unified_progress":[0.036841,0.068153,0.085089,0.096698,0.10067,0.1024,0.10201,0.09845,0.093821,0.088589,0.072299,0.054985]},{"section":6,"text":"That's when the muscles get bigger than usual, which isn't typical unless they're working harder than normal.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.045762,0.069452,0.083205,0.095625,0.10219,0.10487,0.10398,0.097138,0.093538,0.089225,0.071412,0.043598],"unified_progress":[0.04776,0.071057,0.085976,0.09465,0.10002,0.10142,0.099768,0.095837,0.09142,0.082991,0.071522,0.057588]},{"section":7,"text":"Oh, and then there's the high CPK level\u201410,000 IU!","dimen